show.description: Pyaar, dhokha aur ambition ka zabardast fusion shuru hota hai jab taaqatwar khaandaan aapas mein takraate hain. Legacy ke is khel mein purane raaz bahar aate hain… Jo na sirf empires ko hila dete hain, balki dil bhi tod dete hain. Khoon ke rishton aur toote vaadon ke beech — Kya pyaar bachega, ya banega agla nuksaan? Dekhiye ek high-stakes drama jahan emotions gehre hain, wafadaari ki pareeksha hoti hai, Aur har sach ki keemat chukani padti hai.
